\begin_layout Standard
te
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{C}'=\frac{i_{L}}{C}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Napon na zavojnici određuje se izrazom:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{L}=u_{g}-u_{c}-Ri_{L}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

